"you must activate the **Available in POS** setting. To do so, "
"click :guilabel:`Create and edit...` to open the product configuration form. "
"Then, go to the :guilabel:`Sales` tab, tick the :guilabel:`Available in POS` "
"checkbox, and click :guilabel:`Save & Close`."
msgstr ""

