"for the eBay API License Agreement). Fill out :guilabel:`First "
"Name`, :guilabel:`Last Name`, :guilabel:`Email`, :guilabel:`Phone`. Then, "
"select either the :guilabel:`Individual` or :guilabel:`Business` options."
msgstr ""

