"To print the PDF quote, navigate to the confirmed quote, and click "
"the :guilabel:`⚙️ (gear)` icon to reveal a drop-down menu. From this drop-"
"down menu, select :guilabel:`Print`, then select :guilabel:`PDF Quote`."
